  "content": "\n \n \n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0655b669-e3c5-4e41-8c1c-7909e5ea6700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.31203703703703706\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100058353\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0655b669-e3c5-4e41-8c1c-7909e5ea6700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <blockquote style=\"display: block;font-size: 0.9em;overflow: auto;overflow-scrolling: touch;border-left: 3px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);padding-top: 10px;padding-bottom: 10px;border-left-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);margin-top: 1.2em;margin-bottom: 1.2em;padding-right: 1em;padding-left: 1em;border-left-width: 4px;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);quotes: none;\">\n   <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue',\n    'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei',\n    Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\">本期看点：Jack Herrington 揭示服务器函数背后的真相，AI 代理如何构建 AI 代理，自主编码代理的必备功能解析，Zod v4 的重大更新，JavaScript 项目迁移到 TypeScript 的实战经验，Nuxt 和 NuxtLabs 的发展历程，以及那些被认为过时但仍在 2025 年活跃的技术。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"display: block;font-size: 0.9em;overflow: auto;overflow-scrolling: touch;border-left: 3px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);padding-top: 10px;padding-bottom: 10px;border-left-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);margin-top: 1.2em;margin-bottom: 1.2em;padding-right: 1em;padding-left: 1em;border-left-width: 4px;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);quotes: none;\">\n   <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue',\n    'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei',\n    Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：Otto 辛宝、TimLi</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"padding-top:8px;margin:0;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:15px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">PodRocket：服务器函数不存在——对话 Jack Herrington</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- Jack Herrington 揭示服务器函数背后的真相以及它们在 Web 平台上实际上并不存在。深入探讨了 Next.js、TanStack Start 和 Remix 等框架背后的魔法，解析服务器函数如何工作、它们简化了什么、隐藏了什么。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"padding:16px 20px;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.476px;display:flex;font-size:12px;border-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;margin-top:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;align-items:center;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 0 !important;padding-right: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;flex: 1 1 0%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: space-between;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <section>\n     <strong style=\"font-size: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);line-height: 1.75em;font-weight: bold;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\">长按识别二维码查看原文</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;font-size: 12px;margin-bottom: 0;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);word-break: break-all;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\">http://podrocket.logrocket.com/server-functions-dont-exist-jack-herrington</span></p>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;max-width: 90px;box-sizing: border-box;flex-shrink: 0;font-size: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5ccba69e-a80d-48a4-b748-a3a4272afa00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"180\" style=\"margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;display: block;border-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;visibility: visible;width: 90px;\" data-imgfileid=\"100058339\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5ccba69e-a80d-48a4-b748-a3a4272afa00/public\">\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"padding-top:8px;margin:0;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:15px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">破局35岁焦虑：大帅的被动收入秘籍、复利思维与个人IP打造</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 本期我们邀请到一个能折腾的 ITOG-大帅，大帅自称退休程序员，目前已经移居泰国在做出海产品，关注编程，游戏，AI，SEO，营销和增长黑客。大帅将为你揭秘如何通过自媒体和在线教育解锁工作地自由，分享泰国低成本生活的真实魅力，以及国际教育、职场35岁危机的应对策略和打造抗脆弱收入的独家秘籍。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"padding:16px 20px;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.476px;display:flex;font-size:12px;border-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;margin-top:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;align-items:center;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 0 !important;padding-right: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;flex: 1 1 0%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: space-between;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <section>\n     <strong style=\"font-size: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);line-height: 1.75em;font-weight: bold;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\">长按识别二维码查看原文</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;font-size: 12px;margin-bottom: 0;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);word-break: break-all;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://www.xiaoyuzhoufm.com/episode/683f09cd932d829276f7bb7a</span></p>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;max-width: 90px;box-sizing: border-box;flex-shrink: 0;font-size: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dc9962c3-178a-4b42-a4fa-b443a9923200/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"164\" style=\"margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;display: block;border-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;visibility: visible;width: 90px;\" data-imgfileid=\"100058341\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dc9962c3-178a-4b42-a4fa-b443a9923200/public\">\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"padding-top:8px;margin:0;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:15px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">Modern Web：AI 代理构建 AI 代理：Chai.new 内幕</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- Rob Ocel、Danny Thompson 和 Adam Rackis 与 LangBase CEO Ahmad Awais 深入探讨了 Chai.new——一个构建 AI 代理的 AI 代理。Ahmad 分享了为什么在 AI 时代，上下文而非代码才是真正的价值层，以及\"vibe coding\"如何重塑软件构建的参与者范围。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"padding:16px 20px;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.476px;display:flex;font-size:12px;border-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;margin-top:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;align-items:center;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 0 !important;padding-right: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;flex: 1 1 0%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: space-between;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <section>\n     <strong style=\"font-size: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);line-height: 1.75em;font-weight: bold;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\">长按识别二维码查看原文</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;font-size: 12px;margin-bottom: 0;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);word-break: break-all;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://podcasters.spotify.com/pod/show/modern-web/episodes/Building-AI-Agents-That-Build-AI-Agents-Inside-Chai-new-e33pvcm</span></p>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;max-width: 90px;box-sizing: border-box;flex-shrink: 0;font-size: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4f5fe61b-701f-40ef-aa1d-4c82196e3e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"228\" style=\"margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;display: block;border-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;visibility: visible;width: 90px;\" data-imgfileid=\"100058340\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4f5fe61b-701f-40ef-aa1d-4c82196e3e00/public\">\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"padding-top:8px;margin:0;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:15px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">devtools.fm：Peter Pistorius 谈 Redwood SDK</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 与目前掌舵 Redwood 的 Peter Pistorius 对话。Redwood 自首次发布以来经历了很多变化，转向了一个倾向于 React 服务器组件的无服务器框架。Peter 对 Redwood 和个人软件时代的到来有着宏大的愿景。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"padding:16px 20px;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.476px;display:flex;font-size:12px;border-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;margin-top:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;align-items:center;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 0 !important;padding-right: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;flex: 1 1 0%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: space-between;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <section>\n     <strong style=\"font-size: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);line-height: 1.75em;font-weight: bold;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\">长按识别二维码查看原文</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;font-size: 12px;margin-bottom: 0;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);word-break: break-all;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\">https://podcasters.spotify.com/pod/show/devtoolsfm/episodes/Peter-Pistorius---Redwood-SDK-e33lqf6</span></p>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;max-width: 90px;box-sizing: border-box;flex-shrink: 0;font-size: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/733c583d-572b-4a89-546c-40ee538d1c00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" dat